        {
          "step": "Use sector area formula $A = \\frac{1}{2}r^2\\theta$",
          "calculation": "$A = \\frac{1}{2}(8)^2 \\cdot \\frac{\\pi}{4} = \\frac{1}{2} \\cdot 64 \\cdot \\frac{\\pi}{4} = 32 \\cdot \\frac{\\pi}{4} = 8\\pi$ cm²"
